south korea plan 11-12 pct budget rise in 1988 south korea plan to increas the size of it budget in 1988 by 11 to 12 pct from thi year 's 15,596 billion won , econom plan board offici said . the propos boost is base on a govern forecast that gross nation product ( gnp ) will grow by more than 7.5 pct and the gnp deflat by 3.5 pct in 1988 , against target of 8.0 pct and 3.5 pct respect thi year , they said . detail of the 1988 budget , in which spend will match revenu , have yet to be work out , the offici said . the balanc budget in 1986 total 13,800.5 billion won .